00:11:30,132 --> 00:11:31,568
I love that.
  so, no returns.

00:11:31,568 --> 00:11:33,405
You're --
  see, this is what I need,

00:11:33,405 --> 00:11:35,643
is I need the experience,
  and you've done it.

00:11:35,643 --> 00:11:37,748
Well, you're doing really well
  yourself,

00:11:37,748 --> 00:11:39,652
and that's why
  I want to get behind you --

00:11:39,652 --> 00:11:41,923
because sometimes, you just
