00:11:41,923 --> 00:11:43,993
that are doing
  the right thing.
  thank you.

00:11:43,993 --> 00:11:46,231
So, that's my offer.

00:11:46,231 --> 00:11:50,573
That's evaluation of you
  at $300,000.

00:11:50,573 --> 00:11:51,709
That's fair.

00:11:52,844 --> 00:11:54,080
Because you don't make
  any money.

00:11:59,391 --> 00:12:01,162
I think it's too low.

00:12:04,335 --> 00:12:05,503
You know what, Lori?

00:12:05,503 --> 00:12:07,976
Would you be willing
