but they have made
  a counteroffer,

00:12:28,884 --> 00:12:30,187
surprising the sharks.

00:12:30,187 --> 00:12:31,256
You know what, Lori?

00:12:31,256 --> 00:12:33,494
Would you be willing
  to do $120,000 for 20%?

00:12:33,494 --> 00:12:34,429
Ohh!

00:12:36,633 --> 00:12:39,272
We were at $60,000 for 20%.
  CUBAN: Dang!

00:12:39,272 --> 00:12:43,013
So --
